longBusinessSummary: ISA Internationale, Inc., a business development company, provides management consulting services to assist American client companies in complying with the reporting requirements to the government and in communicating with shareholders, customers, and the public, as well as the accessing of needed growth capital. It assists client companies and investments to become public companies. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in St. Paul, Minnesota.
